      "updated": 1644712280
    },
    {
      "id": "6208515832ef92000078bc79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712280,
      "updated": 1644712280
    },
    {
      "id": "6208514932ef92000078bc76",
      "text": "[https://oidon5.hatenablog.com/entry/2020/05/30/160000 おもしろき こともなき世を（に） おもしろく すみなすものは 心なりけり - おいどんブログ]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712265,
      "updated": 1644712271
    },
    {
      "id": "6208514e32ef92000078bc77",
      "text": ">晋作「世の中ってのは、面白くないものよ。でもそれを面白く過ごすのが大事なのさ。」",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712271,
      "updated": 1644712413
    },
    {
      "id": "620851dd32ef92000078bc7f",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712413,
      "updated": 1644712413
    },
    {
      "id": "620851dd32ef92000078bc80",
      "text": "> [望東尼]「そう。面白くするのは、あたなの心次第。」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1644712413,
      "updated": 1666619841
    },
    {
      "id": "620851dd32ef92000078bc81",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712413,
      "updated": 1644712413
    },
    {
      "id": "620851dd32ef92000078bc82",
      "text": "> 「世の中はただ目の前に存在し、時は滔々と流れていくの。それをどう捉えるか。あなたの心が毎日を面白くもつまらなくもするのよ。」",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712413,
      "updated": 1644712413
    },
    {
      "id": "620851dd32ef92000078bc83",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712413,
      "updated": 1644712413
    },
    {
      "id": "620851dd32ef92000078bc84",
      "text": "> という掛け合いのようです。",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712413,
      "updated": 1644712413
    },
    {
      "id": "620851da32ef92000078bc7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712411,
      "updated": 1644712412
    },
    {
      "id": "6208519832ef92000078bc7c",
      "text": "\t[高杉晋作]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712344,
      "updated": 1644712353
    },
    {
      "id": "6208519932ef92000078bc7d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712345,
      "updated": 1644712345
    },
    {
      "id": "6208518032ef92000078bc7a",
      "text": "\tこの世界は面白くなかったのか",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712321,
      "updated": 1644712343
    },
    {
      "id": "6208518132ef92000078bc7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712322,
      "updated": 1644712322
    },
    {
      "id": "620851b0a3368200004203f1",
      "text": "\t[Twitterのbio]に入ってると嫌な文字列TOP3に入る",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1644712368,
      "updated": 1644717285
    },
    {
      "id": "620851b4a3368200004203f2",
      "text": "\t\t>[https://twitter.com/tnayuki/status/1486589111037497345?s=20&t=eF1Vw2swx67GLMMaPXNbKg tnayuki(@tnayuki)]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712372,
      "updated": 1644712427
    },
    {
      "id": "620851ea32ef92000078bc86",
      "text": "  >おっさんTwitter道",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712427,
      "updated": 1644712427
    },
    {
      "id": "620851ea32ef92000078bc87",
      "text": "  >1. 自分語りしない",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712427,
      "updated": 1644712427
    },
    {
      "id": "620851ea32ef92000078bc88",
      "text": "  >2. 面識ない相手に話しかけない",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712427,
      "updated": 1644712427
    },
    {
      "id": "620851ea32ef92000078bc89",
      "text": "  >3. プロフィールに「[おもしろきこともなき世をおもしろく]」って書かない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1644712427,
      "updated": 1657106814
    },
    {
      "id": "620851e632ef92000078bc85",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712423,
      "updated": 1644712423
    },
    {
      "id": "620851ed32ef92000078bc8a",
      "text": "\t\t\t別にそうでもない気もする",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712430,
      "updated": 1644712439
    },
    {
      "id": "620851f932ef92000078bc8c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tわざわざTOP3にあげることかな？と思っちゃった",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712442,
      "updated": 1644712456
    },
    {
      "id": "6208520832ef92000078bc8d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tオチの意味もあったのかも知れないけど",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712456,
      "updated": 1644712472
    },
    {
      "id": "620851f132ef92000078bc8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712434,
      "updated": 1644712434
    },
    {
      "id": "6208523b32ef92000078bc8e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://twitter.com/tnayuki/status/1487090200371404804?s=20&t=eF1Vw2swx67GLMMaPXNbKg tnayuki(@tnayuki)]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712509,
      "updated": 1644712514
    },
    {
      "id": "6208524132ef92000078bc90",
      "text": "   >これ自戒のつもりで書いたのがじわじわ拡散してるんで補足ですが、1.は空気読まなかったり度を越してなければ、2.は相手にリスペクトがあればOKだと思います！",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712514,
      "updated": 1644712514
    },
    {
      "id": "6208524132ef92000078bc91",
      "text": "   >あと20代30代の若者はこんなこと気にせずガンガン行くといいと思います！ちな当方はおっさんです。",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1644712514,
      "updated": 1644712514
    },
    {
      "id": "64b87ebb5e90c0000094b95d",
      "text": "   #Twitterのbioに入ってると嫌な文字列",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1689812667,
      "updated": 1689812683
    },
    {
      "id": "6208523f32ef92000078bc8f",
      "text": " [/vim-jp-emojis/zenzen-wakaranai.icon][takker.icon][kuuote.icon]",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1644712512,
      "updated": 1644718417
    },
    {
      "id": "620868e91280f00000020aac",
      "text": "  わからないのは単純にTwitter communicationの文脈を全く知らないからだろうけど",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1644718313,
      "updated": 1644718351
    },
    {
      "id": "620868e11280f00000020aab",
      "text": "  Twitterに入り浸ってるけど聞いたことすらなかった[kuuote.icon]",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1644718305,
      "updated": 1644718474
    },
    {
      "id": "6208698a4bb2e20000cb231e",
      "text": "   面白そうな人フォローしてると自然と対象から外れるのかも",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1644718474,
      "updated": 1644718493
    },
    {
      "id": "6208529432ef92000078bc92",
      "text": "　あー、わかる、わかる [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1644712597,
      "updated": 1644723576
    },
    {
      "id": "62087d7f5b98c2000069ad3f",
      "text": "  この 「おもしろきこともなき世をおもしろく」というのは、典型的な[おじさん構文]だね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1644723584,
      "updated": 1644723673
    },
    {
      "id": "62087df35b98c2000069ad41",
      "text": "  自分の blog のタイトルを「[徒然草]」にしちゃうおじさんとかと同類のスメルがする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1644723700,
      "updated": 1644723784
    },
    {
      "id": "64b8d8fac505840000b3bb83",
      "text": " わかる[kumatako.icon]",
      "userId": "647c8b9395c05d001cc50584",
      "created": 1689835770,
      "updated": 1689835855
    },
    {
      "id": "64b8d94fc505840000b3bb87",
      "text": " \t無理に面白い（と思いこんでること）を言いたそうな感じ",
      "userId": "647c8b9395c05d001cc50584",
      "created": 1689835855,
      "updated": 1689835915
    },
    {
      "id": "64b8d965c505840000b3bb88",
      "text": " \tちょっと教養ひけらかし感もある",
      "userId": "647c8b9395c05d001cc50584",
      "created": 1689835877,
      "updated": 1689835888
    },
    {
      "id": "62089564e5172d00003c409a",
      "text": " [日日是好日]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1644729700,
      "updated": 1644729715
    },
    {
      "id": "62087d855b98c2000069ad40",
